    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car. This ride has been such a reliable companion and is still in wonderful shape for its next owner! It's been well-loved, drives super smoothly, and is ready to hit the road for many more adventures. If you're looking for a dependable vehicle that's been treated with care, you've found it! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions at all\u2014I'd love to see this go to a great new home!",
      "price": 31500.0,
