    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the S65B40 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to produce a linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission provides lightning-fast gear synchronization, paired with the M Variable Differential Lock for superior lateral traction. This example features a reinforced subframe and has undergone rod bearing prophylaxis to ensure long-term reciprocating assembly integrity. The suspension retains its factory-spec Electronic Damper Control (EDC), offering precise damping adjustments. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains in peak operating condition with no signs of thermal stress or fluid cavitation.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Clean title. Maintenance records available. Minor cosmetic wear. Runs and drives without issues.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW M2, finished in striking Long Beach Blue Metallic. This car has been a joy to own and has been treated with the utmost care. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like shine, though there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and hood from spirited weekend drives. The interior is upholstered in Black Dakota leather with blue contrast stitching; the cabin remains fresh and smoke-free, with only slight wear visible on the driver\u2019s side seat bolster. Mechanically, this vehicle is in great shape. It comes with a complete service history, having recently received a fresh oil change and a new set of spark plugs. The tires are Michelin Pilot Super Sports with approximately 70% tread remaining. All electronics, including the navigation system and the premium Harman Kardon audio, function exactly as they should. This M2 offers a pure driving experience and is ready for its next owner to take it through the gears. Included are both sets of keys and all original owner's manuals.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, which exemplifies a commitment to consistent maintenance and mechanical excellence. This unit has undergone a comprehensive professional inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for performance and reliability. Featuring a refined interior and a robust service history, this vehicle offers an exceptional opportunity for the sophisticated driver seeking quality without compromise. We invite you to experience its superior handling and well-preserved aesthetics firsthand.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It's been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape! It runs beautifully and has been well-taken care of over the years. This is the perfect match for someone looking for a dependable vehicle that\u2019s ready to hit the road today. I've loved driving this beauty, and I'm sure you will too\u2014come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
