      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine and a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox. This example delivers exceptional mechanical feedback through its individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Crucial maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure long-term structural and engine timing reliability. The factory limited-slip differential provides excellent traction out of corners, while the suspension geometry remains true to its original M-division specifications. While showing honest signs of use, the drivetrain is robust, and the throttle response is razor-sharp. A true analog masterpiece for the discerning pilot.",
